OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, When Dylan Davies went to check his    
OL,6, post last November, 580 brown envelopes
OL,7, fell to the floor.                     
OL,9,FOver next six months he got tax bills  
OL,10,Ffor 11,000 Chinese companies after they
OL,11,Ffraudulently used his Cardiff address  
OL,12,Fto register for VAT.                   
OL,14,F"It's been horrendous," said Mr Davies,
OL,15,Fwho got letters from HM Revenue &      
OL,16,FCustoms (HMRC) demanding tax amounting 
OL,17,Fto #500,000.                           
OL,19,FHMRC admitted the situation did not    
OL,20,Fraise alarm bells at the tax office.   
